<emphasis id="21C71DA6F8A0D83C3414ED369EA3A724" italics="true" pageNumber="276">Sect.</emphasis>
Allium
</taxonomicName>
: 144. 1996), who acknowledges that, because of its type, 
<taxonomicName id="5F535922D3D4E9ED118E101F981A71FF" authority="L." authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1756" class="Liliopsida" family="Amaryllidaceae" genus="Allium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ascalonicum">
<emphasis id="F5014F2C9542A763038B08E0F36002C6" italics="true" pageNumber="276">A. ascalonicum</emphasis>
